      "author_association" : "NONE",
      "body" : "I got a third application that failed, so I decided it was just easier to fix the block file.\ndd bs=1 if=blk00000.dat of=genesis.dat count=293\ndd bs=586 if=blk00000.dat of=tail.dat skip=1\ncat genesis.dat genesis.dat tail.dat >blk00000.dat\n",
